OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775127601
OL,3,CMore than a dozen goldfinches and
OL,4,Ccanaries snatched in burglary
OL,6,FMore than a dozen birds have been
OL,7,Fstolen from an outdoor aviary at a
OL,8,Fhome in North Dorset.
OL,10,FFour pairs of canaries and 12 northern
OL,11,Fgoldfinches were taken from an address
OL,12,Fnear Underdown Hollow in Bradford
OL,13,FAbbas between Saturday (21 March)
OL,14,Fnight and early Sunday (22nd March)
OL,15,Fmorning.
OL,17,FDorset Police Officers are asking
OL,18,Fanyone with information or who
OL,19,Fwitnessed the burglary to come forward
OL,20,Fwith more information.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
