OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775127601
OL,3,CMore than a dozen goldfinches and
OL,4,Ccanaries snatched in burglary
OL,6,FPolice Constable Sebastian Haggett
OL,7,Ffrom Dorset Police's Rural Crime Team
OL,8,Fsaid, "We are carrying out a full
OL,9,Finvestigation into this incident and I
OL,10,Fam keen to hear from anyone who
OL,11,Fwitnessed any suspicious activity in
OL,12,Fthe area during the relevant time
OL,13,Fperiod."
OL,15,FThe force is asking for any homes in
OL,16,Fthe area to check to see if they have
OL,17,Fany footage from that weekend.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
