PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775127601
OL,3,CMore than a dozen goldfinches and
OL,4,Ccanaries snatched in burglary
OL,6,FConstable Haggett added: "I would also
OL,7,Furge residents in the vicinity with
OL,8,Fhome CCTV or doorbell cameras to
OL,9,Fplease review their footage for
OL,10,Fanything that might assist our
OL,11,Fenquiries.
OL,13,F"Finally, if you have information as
OL,14,Fto where the stolen birds are, please
OL,15,Fcome forward so we can reunite them
OL,16,Fwith their owner."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
